<title>POLAND: KROSNO MARCH NET FALLS TO PLN 0.5 MLN.</title>
<headline>KROSNO MARCH NET FALLS TO PLN 0.5 MLN.</headline>
<dateline>WARSAW 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Preliminary results March </p>
<p>(in million zlotys unless stated)</p>
<p>MARCH</p>
<p> Net profit	     0.47 vs   1.04</p>
<p> Pre-tax profit	 0.74 vs   1.73</p>
<p> Operating profit     1.07 vs   1.94</p>
<p> Sales		   16.13 vs  16.44</p>
